City of
Joburg’s MMC of Health and Social Development, Dr Mpho Phalatse, has noted the
high rate of TB-infected patients dropping out of TB treatments with great
concern.This was
after World TB Day was commemorated on 24 March.According
to Dr Phalatse, out of the 14 648 TB cases tracked by the City’s Heath
